{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Grid Areas","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>网格区域</strong>是网格中由一个或者多个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Grid_Cell\">网格单元格</a>组成的一个矩形区域。当你使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Line-based_Placement_with_CSS_Grid\">基于网格线位置</a>放置一个项目或者使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">命名的网格区域</a>定义区域时，网格区域被创建。</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas/1_grid_area.png\" alt=\"Image showing a highlighted grid area\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>本质上，网格区域一定是矩形的。例如，不可能创建 T 形或 L 形的网格区域。</p>\n<p>在下面的例子中，有一个网格容器包含两个网格项目，我用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\"><code>grid-area</code></a> 属性命名它们，然后用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code></a> 把它们放在网格上。这将创建两个网格区域，一个覆盖四个网格单元格，另外一个覆盖两个。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css hidden notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">*</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token property\">box-sizing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> border-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.wrapper</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px solid #f76707<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff4e6<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.wrapper &gt; div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px solid #ffa94d<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">border-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 5px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #ffd8a8<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #d9480f<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.wrapper</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> grid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-columns</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-rows</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px 100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-template-areas</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"a a b\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"a a b\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.item1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-area</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.item2</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">grid-area</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> b<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>wrapper<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n   <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>item2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"示例 sample\" id=\"frame_示例\" width=\"300\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas/_sample_.%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性参考","title":"属性参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\"><code>grid-auto-rows</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\"><code>grid-template-areas</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\"><code>grid-area</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"扩展阅读","title":"扩展阅读","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>CSS Grid Layout Guide: <em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">Basic concepts of grid layout</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Grid Layout Guide: <em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">Grid template areas</a></em></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid/#grid-area-concept\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Definition of Grid Areas in the CSS Grid Layout specification</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"网格区域是网格中由一个或者多个网格单元格组成的一个矩形区域。当你使用基于网格线位置放置一个